00:19:22.584 --> 00:19:24.784
But it's all bad occasions.

317
00:19:25.223 --> 00:19:26.384
You did good.

318
00:19:27.653 --> 00:19:29.153
But I don't like the articles.

319
00:19:29.393 --> 00:19:32.824
