00:19:44.544 --> 00:19:45.703
I'm getting hot.

325
00:19:46.243 --> 00:19:47.814
- Should I open the window? - Yes.

326
00:19:49.643 --> 00:19:51.584
Your menopause came too late.

327
00:19:51.584 --> 00:19:53.453
Let's take something for your headache.

328
00:19:54.084 --> 00:19:55.784
I don't like taking pills.

329
00:19:55.784 --> 00:19:57.524
I guess I have to take one since you're telling me to.

330
00:19:58.483 --> 00:19:59.993
I like that you always listen to me.

331
00:20:01.753 --> 00:20:03.264
Let's go eat something good for dinner.

332
00:20:03.624 --> 00:20:05.764
Yes, let's go somewhere nice.

333
00:20:06.094 --> 00:20:07.794
There are a lot of good restaurants in this neighborhood.

334
00:20:09.433 --> 00:20:11.804
I know a good place. Let's go there.

335
00:20:15.203 --> 00:20:16.604
We saw profit this month.

336
00:20:20.114 --> 00:20:22.673
So Good Soup is on its way to success?

337
00:20:22.844 --> 00:20:26.243
I won't have to worry about letting the employees go at least.

338
00:20:26.713 --> 00:20:27.814
I should get going.

339
00:20:28.554 --> 00:20:30.423
What are you doing tomorrow? You're off tomorrow too.

340
00:20:30.753 --> 00:20:31.854
I don't have plans.

341
00:20:32.753 --> 00:20:34.094
Let's hang out. It's been a while.

342
00:20:34.693 --> 00:20:36.963
Shouldn't you hang out with the person you're going to propose to?

343
00:20:40.134 --> 00:20:41.794
She's not in a situation to do that right now.

344
00:20:42.264 --> 00:20:45.703
Is she even real? I've never seen you with someone.

345
00:20:46.104 --> 00:20:48.173
I always do those things alone.

346
00:20:49.233 --> 00:20:50.604
Just get ready to greet her.

347
00:20:51.344 --> 00:20:52.604
I'll look forward to it.

348
00:20:53.473 --> 00:20:54.614
But where are you going now?

349
00:20:54.874 --> 00:20:57.814
Writer Lee Hyun Soo. She's dropping out of "Unruly Detectives".

350
00:20:57.913 --> 00:20:59.884
I'm very busy sorting that out.

351
00:21:02.054 --> 00:21:03.653
You guys decided on that in the end?

352
00:21:03.753 --> 00:21:05.983
Yes. That's what she decided.

353
00:21:06.594 --> 00:21:07.624
I'm taking off.

354
00:21:19.003 --> 00:21:21.074
(Restaurant closed.)

355
00:21:21.074 --> 00:21:22.774
(Restaurant closed on every Sunday and Monday.)

356
00:21:24.943 --> 00:21:27.143
This is where I wanted to take you guys.

357
00:21:29.544 --> 00:21:30.544
Good Soup?

358
00:21:31.044 --> 00:21:32.284
What a pretty name.

359
00:21:33.014 --> 00:21:34.753
Why did they have to close today?

360
00:21:34.953 --> 00:21:36.624
I know.

361
00:21:37.453 --> 00:21:38.653
It doesn't suit us.

362
00:21:38.653 --> 00:21:41.723
That's not true. You have no logic.

363
00:21:41.723 --> 00:21:43.893
What does logic have to do here?

364
00:21:43.893 --> 00:21:45.824
Why can't I think like that?

365
00:21:46.663 --> 00:21:50.304
You always make me mad even when I try to be nice.

366
00:21:50.403 --> 00:21:53.163
When have you ever tried to be nice?

367
00:21:53.703 --> 00:21:54.703
Stop it.

368
00:21:55.703 --> 00:21:58.243
Seeing your children fight in front of your eyes...

369
00:21:58.903 --> 00:22:00.374
is the most upsetting thing as a parent.

370
00:22:02.913 --> 00:22:04.213
I'm sorry, dad.

371
00:22:04.213 --> 00:22:05.614
I'm sorry, dad.

372
00:22:06.243 --> 00:22:07.413
(Restaurant closed.)

373
00:22:07.784 --> 00:22:09.054
- Let's go somewhere else. - Let's go somewhere else.

374
00:22:09.054 --> 00:22:10.054
Let's go.

375
00:22:26.003 --> 00:22:28.274
You're such a workaholic. It's our day off.

376
00:22:29.403 --> 00:22:31.203
- What's that? - Brine.

377
00:22:31.443 --> 00:22:33.044
Brining normally takes too long.

378
00:22:34.814 --> 00:22:36.743
You exceed me, Sous-chef.

379
00:22:36.943 --> 00:22:38.544
It's nothing, Chef.

380
00:22:39.743 --> 00:22:42.384
But you can make knife marks. Do you need the syringe?

381
00:22:42.483 --> 00:22:44.854
The syringe speeds it up and evens it out.

382
00:22:46.024 --> 00:22:49.024
I guess if you make holes, the seasoning seeps in better.

383
00:22:49.223 --> 00:22:50.223
You're quick.

384
00:22:50.594 --> 00:22:53.124
And it also lets the fat seep out more.

385
00:22:54.393 --> 00:22:55.493
Who are you making this for?

386
00:22:56.463 --> 00:22:57.733
I asked Hong Ah to come.

387
00:22:59.433 --> 00:23:01.534
Don't hate her too much.

388
00:23:02.074 --> 00:23:04.643
I know she's self-centered and selfish.

389
00:23:05.074 --> 00:23:07.544
She's too focused on her own desires to be considerate of others.

390
00:23:08.443 --> 00:23:10.943
Why would I hate her? It's none of my business.

391
00:23:11.943 --> 00:23:13.413
Love takes many forms.

392
00:23:14.453 --> 00:23:16.753
You and Hyun Soo aren't normal either.

393
00:23:19.423 --> 00:23:21.723
I want her to be in a normal relationship.

394
00:23:21.824 --> 00:23:24.893
Me too. I want that for Hyun Soo.

395
00:23:25.864 --> 00:23:27.663
You don't have to worry about Hyun Soo.

396
00:23:27.663 --> 00:23:30.134
She's the type to check again and again.

397
00:23:30.463 --> 00:23:31.634
She can't make mistakes.

398
00:23:33.334 --> 00:23:34.374
You're right.

399
00:23:35.034 --> 00:23:37.443
I get to retire next year.

400
00:23:37.544 --> 00:23:38.804
I don't have much time left.

401
00:23:39.804 --> 00:23:41.344
Let's just wait a bit more and hang in there.

402
00:23:41.643 --> 00:23:44.314
We get a pension, and we can collect our savings.

403
00:23:44.643 --> 00:23:46.114
All that's left is to have fun.

404
00:23:46.114 --> 00:23:47.514
If it's with you,

405
00:23:48.213 --> 00:23:50.084
waiting is fun too.

406
00:23:52.524 --> 00:23:54.524
Everyone said it wasn't good,

407
00:23:54.524 --> 00:23:56.253
but I enjoyed "Unruly Detectives".

408
00:23:56.993 --> 00:23:58.024
I could sympathize.

409
00:23:58.723 --> 00:24:00.034
It's about us.

410
00:24:00.534 --> 00:24:02.864
Right? It is about us, right?

411
00:24:04.634 --> 00:24:07.733
But hey, am I really that mean?

412
00:24:08.134 --> 00:24:10.203
Betraying his own brother for his career...

413
00:24:10.203 --> 00:24:12.544
If you were in the situation, you'd do the same without hesitation.

414
00:24:13.844 --> 00:24:15.713
But the director was bad at that.

415
00:24:16.274 --> 00:24:18.044
He didn't know how to build up the story.

416
00:24:18.284 --> 00:24:20.354
The theme seems to sibling love.

417
00:24:20.354 --> 00:24:22.983
But he shot it as an action show. All they do is fight and crash.

418
00:24:23.423 --> 00:24:24.723
I like you.

419
00:24:25.524 --> 00:24:27.524
I can almost forget all the horrible things you did to me.

420
00:24:27.753 --> 00:24:28.753
Horrible things?

421
00:24:29.124 --> 00:24:30.564
What an awful word to use.

422
00:24:32.024 --> 00:24:35.334
Just know that your family will always be...

423
00:24:35.364 --> 00:24:36.903
the last people standing for you.

424
00:24:43.243 --> 00:24:46.304
("Kind Soup Will Not Pick up His Calls")

425
00:24:53.683 --> 00:24:54.884
Jung Woo, I'm here.

426
00:24:56.384 --> 00:24:57.423
You're here early.

427
00:24:57.923 --> 00:24:58.983
Didn't you shoot the drama today?

428
00:24:59.584 --> 00:25:01.723
We're not shooting tomorrow either. The script isn't ready yet.

429
00:25:02.153 --> 00:25:04.223
I'm sure it's not easy to continue what someone else had started.

430
00:25:04.893 --> 00:25:05.893
Why did you ask to see me?

431
00:25:07.064 --> 00:25:08.094
Have you ever read this script?

432
00:25:08.094 --> 00:25:09.134
("Kind Soup Will Not Pick up His Calls")

433
00:25:09.834 --> 00:25:11.903
It's written by Hyun Soo.

434
00:25:12.104 --> 00:25:13.304
I heard about it.

435
00:25:14.173 --> 00:25:15.574
The main character is a chef,

436
00:25:15.574 --> 00:25:17.374
and Kind Soup is his online nickname.

437
00:25:17.774 --> 00:25:19.304
She wrote this before she wrote "Unruly Detectives".

438
00:25:19.304 --> 00:25:20.443
I like this one.

439
00:25:21.774 --> 00:25:23.284
I should produce a drama with this script.

440
00:25:23.483 --> 00:25:24.943
Isn't this a melodrama?

441
00:25:25.314 --> 00:25:26.884
I think I told you to forgot it.

442
00:25:27.953 --> 00:25:30.084
But this one has its own unique color.

443
00:25:30.784 --> 00:25:32.824
I think it would do well on a cable channel.

444
00:25:34.124 --> 00:25:37.294
You're really incredible. I'm so moved by your efforts.

445
00:25:38.024 --> 00:25:40.893
You stayed by the side of a woman who's not interested in you,

446
00:25:40.893 --> 00:25:42.134
and opened up opportunities for her.

447
00:25:42.693 --> 00:25:45.134
Jung Woo, can't you do the same for me too?

448
00:25:46.334 --> 00:25:47.834
Why are you so talkative?

449
00:25:50.903 --> 00:25:52.874
I want to direct this.

450
00:25:54.173 --> 00:25:55.874
Your work is really difficult to understand.

451
00:25:56.213 --> 00:25:59.183
That's because I never chose what I wanted to direct.

452
00:25:59.183 --> 00:26:00.713
I just directed what the upper management told me to.

453
00:26:00.814 --> 00:26:02.653
I want to direct this. Let me direct this.

454
00:26:02.884 --> 00:26:04.453
I want to try working with Hyun Soo.

455
00:26:11.163 --> 00:26:12.764
(Director Kim Joon Ha)

456
00:26:15.493 --> 00:26:16.663
Hey, Director Kim.

457
00:26:17.433 --> 00:26:18.503
How have you been?

458
00:26:20.233 --> 00:26:22.074
Just get to the point.

459
00:26:22.134 --> 00:26:23.874
You don't need to be formal and ask me how I'm doing.

460
00:26:23.874 --> 00:26:26.614
My gosh, why are you so cold?

461
00:26:26.614 --> 00:26:28.514
Your making me heart ache even more.

462
00:26:29.143 --> 00:26:31.183
Did you just say I made your heart ache even more?

463
00:26:31.913 --> 00:26:34.314
I can't believe you still use that pick up line.

464
00:26:34.453 --> 00:26:36.753
Why would I even try to seduce you?

465
00:26:36.884 --> 00:26:39.384
I'm not saying you're trying to seduce me.

466
00:26:39.854 --> 00:26:42.094
I'm just saying you're used to using pick-up lines all the time.

467
00:26:42.153 --> 00:26:44.463
Okay, whatever. I'm on my way to your studio right now.

468
00:26:44.594 --> 00:26:46.364
I'm going to barge in, so don't be surprised.

469
00:26:46.524 --> 00:26:49.733
Do whatever you want. I'm not there anyway.

470
00:26:50.534 --> 00:26:51.733
Are you with Hyun Soo right now?

471
00:26:52.233 --> 00:26:54.703
