472
00:26:54.973 --> 00:26:57.074
Hyun Soo and I aren't going to be in Seoul starting from tomorrow.

473
00:27:09.054 --> 00:27:10.054
How does it taste?

474
00:27:11.453 --> 00:27:12.453
It's delicious.

475
00:27:12.653 --> 00:27:14.693
It's crispy on the outside, and it's moist on the inside.

476
00:27:14.693 --> 00:27:15.953
The texture is also great.

477
00:27:17.094 --> 00:27:19.463
Chef, I'll always be loyal to you.

478
00:27:26.604 --> 00:27:27.834
You're here.

479
00:27:28.134 --> 00:27:29.574
What's he doing here?

480
00:27:30.044 --> 00:27:32.874
You called me over to give me food, but I'm about to lose my appetite.

481
00:27:34.143 --> 00:27:36.344
I'll leave now, so that you can save your appetite.

482
00:27:36.743 --> 00:27:39.014
Since when were you so considerate?

483
00:27:39.713 --> 00:27:40.814
Just focus on what you need to.

484
00:27:40.814 --> 00:27:43.683
Hong Ah, you're really good at criticizing people.

485
00:27:43.683 --> 00:27:45.423
I'm not criticizing anyone. I'm just stating the facts.

486
00:27:47.324 --> 00:27:48.824
Do you know that Hyun Soo got fired?

487
00:27:48.993 --> 00:27:50.864
Her career might've just ended.

488
00:27:51.524 --> 00:27:52.564
Is it that bad?

489
00:27:52.663 --> 00:27:54.134
She's not persistent at all.

490
00:27:54.294 --> 00:27:57.264
She went through so much to get to where she is right now.

491
00:27:57.604 --> 00:28:00.733
Someone might think you actually care for her.

492
00:28:02.074 --> 00:28:04.844
You must be upset now that she's in a bad situation.

493
00:28:05.574 --> 00:28:08.374
I hope you suffer a lot because of her.

494
00:28:09.243 --> 00:28:12.913
Okay. I'll fulfill your wish and suffer a lot because of her.

495
00:28:13.554 --> 00:28:15.153
I'll also love her a lot as well.

496
00:28:34.774 --> 00:28:35.774
What's your name?

497
00:28:36.433 --> 00:28:38.774
I'm going to turn down your offer.

498
00:28:39.473 --> 00:28:40.473
Will you wait for me?

499
00:28:41.473 --> 00:28:43.114
Love is so meaningless.

500
00:28:43.443 --> 00:28:46.213
I can't waste my youth on something like that.

501
00:28:47.384 --> 00:28:48.784
I won't go if you tell me not to go.

502
00:28:49.354 --> 00:28:52.054
You don't need to put a meaning behind an irresponsible kiss.

503
00:28:52.524 --> 00:28:54.524
I wasn't being clingy.

504
00:28:54.524 --> 00:28:55.524
(On Jung Sun)

505
00:28:57.923 --> 00:28:59.163
I'm not going to pick up.

506
00:29:00.034 --> 00:29:02.294
I didn't know you were so rash.

507
00:29:02.534 --> 00:29:04.834
How could I check with you when you didn't even pick up my call?

508
00:29:04.834 --> 00:29:06.874
When did I not pick up?

509
00:29:10.344 --> 00:29:11.844
You didn't think you'd get rejected, did you?

510
00:29:11.903 --> 00:29:14.114
Do you think everything will be fine if you tell me that you regret it?

511
00:29:14.314 --> 00:29:16.243
You can't turn back time.

512
00:29:16.243 --> 00:29:18.284
Do you think I had fun during that time?

513
00:29:30.993 --> 00:29:32.723
You'll get tired if you take a break.

514
00:29:32.923 --> 00:29:34.433
You need to force yourself to keep running.

515
00:29:34.933 --> 00:29:35.933
I know that.

516
00:29:36.604 --> 00:29:37.733
If you know, you need to put that into action.

517
00:29:37.834 --> 00:29:38.933
- Okay. - Keep running.

518
00:29:39.064 --> 00:29:40.733
If your legs feel too heavy,

519
00:29:41.074 --> 00:29:42.534
you should consciously move your arms.

520
00:29:42.534 --> 00:29:44.344
- Like this? - Yes, that's great.

521
00:29:44.473 --> 00:29:45.544
Now, go forward.

522
00:29:46.203 --> 00:29:48.213
Gosh, I'm sorry. You can go first. I'll go by myself.

523
00:29:49.413 --> 00:29:51.344
It's a great day to commit murder.

524
00:29:51.544 --> 00:29:52.814
Who are you going to murder?

525
00:29:53.183 --> 00:29:54.614
It's the homework I got from the main writer.

526
00:29:56.453 --> 00:29:57.453
Do you want to go out with me?

527
00:29:58.284 --> 00:30:00.054
My gosh, you startled me.

528
00:30:00.324 --> 00:30:02.453
It's nothing compared to how startled I was.

529
00:30:02.524 --> 00:30:03.993
Why are you angry at me?

530
00:30:03.993 --> 00:30:05.193
Because it's you.

531
00:30:05.193 --> 00:30:07.594
Why are you angry at me? And why are you teasing me?

532
00:30:07.663 --> 00:30:10.564
I almost hugged you because I was so happy to see you.

533
00:30:27.983 --> 00:30:29.514
You're incredible.

534
00:30:30.683 --> 00:30:32.324
How did you manage to break through this wall?

535
00:30:38.094 --> 00:30:40.364
I promise that I'll live like you.

536
00:31:00.014 --> 00:31:02.753
- Why aren't you sleeping yet? - My gosh.

537
00:31:04.453 --> 00:31:06.024
It's not time for me to sleep yet.

538
00:31:07.124 --> 00:31:08.423
You seem okay.

539
00:31:09.124 --> 00:31:10.463
There's no reason for me not to be okay.

540
00:31:11.423 --> 00:31:12.594
I saw the article.

541
00:31:14.393 --> 00:31:18.104
"Writer Lee Hyun Soo had to drop out due to health concerns."

542
00:31:18.804 --> 00:31:20.233
You talk as if it has nothing to do with you.

543
00:31:20.403 --> 00:31:21.903
It doesn't have anything to do with me anymore.

544
00:31:23.203 --> 00:31:25.044
It's always hard to come to a decision.

545
00:31:25.143 --> 00:31:27.274
But once I do, I never turn back.

546
00:31:28.443 --> 00:31:30.084
It seems like you're going through a rough time,

547
00:31:30.183 --> 00:31:31.683
so I'll bear with the boasting.

548
00:31:38.483 --> 00:31:39.923
I'm going on a trip tomorrow.

549
00:31:41.054 --> 00:31:42.124
With... With whom?

550
00:31:43.153 --> 00:31:45.564
With Kyung. You saw her once.

551
00:31:49.034 --> 00:31:51.703
She went through a lot while working with me.

552
00:31:52.034 --> 00:31:53.304
I want to show her a good time.

553
00:32:13.354 --> 00:32:14.753
(On Jung Sun)

554
00:32:15.953 --> 00:32:16.993
Hey.

555
00:32:17.564 --> 00:32:20.134
Jung Woo, can I cancel on our appointment tomorrow?

556
00:32:21.064 --> 00:32:23.804
You're making it hard for me to refuse.

557
00:32:24.334 --> 00:32:25.364
I'm sorry.

558
00:32:25.604 --> 00:32:28.574
I asked you out in a really long time, but you just rejected me.

559
00:32:28.733 --> 00:32:30.274
Are you doing this because you've become a hot shot?

560
00:32:31.003 --> 00:32:32.844
I'll pay you back tenfold.

561
00:32:33.413 --> 00:32:35.114
You better.

562
00:32:42.713 --> 00:32:44.183
What are you doing here? I thought you were leaving.

563
00:32:44.183 --> 00:32:45.223
Sit down.

564
00:32:47.824 --> 00:32:50.193
Jung Woo, it's time to take action.

565
00:32:50.294 --> 00:32:51.663
You've been watching her for too long.

566
00:32:52.124 --> 00:32:55.064
Hyun Soo probably wants you to make the first move.

567
00:32:55.893 --> 00:32:57.304
I don't agree with you.

568
00:32:57.304 --> 00:32:58.804
My gosh, trust me on this.

569
00:32:59.163 --> 00:33:00.203
What are you doing tomorrow?

570
00:33:01.034 --> 00:33:03.173
My appointment for tomorrow just got canceled.

571
00:33:04.503 --> 00:33:05.574
This is fate.

572
00:33:06.003 --> 00:33:09.544
I'll be the bridge to help you and Hyun Soo get together.

573
00:33:10.314 --> 00:33:12.544
Can you be clear, so that I can understand?

574
00:33:13.354 --> 00:33:15.054
I'm saying we should meet Hyun Soo tomorrow.

575
00:33:15.153 --> 00:33:16.653
Let's meet her accidentally on purpose.

576
00:33:22.393 --> 00:33:25.564
(Episode 16 will air shortly.)

